snippet.title: Sapphire Hotel - The Little Tales of: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Hotel is now open! Explore every room interacting with all who stays there. Unveil the mystery of who stole the cat’s-eye Sapphire. In this unique story driven blue world! Available for Gameboy and the Analogue Pocket!

Welcome to sapphire hotel. The stand alone sequel to Alexandra With redefined interactivity, and massively improved graphics.

Game page: 
https://authormre.itch.io/sapphire-hotel-the-little-tales-of

-------------------------------------------------------------------
Itch page: https://authormre.itch.io/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/authormre
